":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:52:00.000Z","msg":"其實好多警察比香港喪，特別係生蕃地方，印尼嗰度一場足球騷亂可以發射三百幾粒催淚彈，打傷幾百人，不過班球迷都可以癲，燒哂現場所有警車，打死兩個猜佬，所以你唔喪啲，真係制唔到嗰啲人。<br />\n<br />\n其實重點係香港示威者已經比較溫和，嗰啲掟嘢，人哋國家嘅人見你居然只係掟安全帽同水樽，有啲仲要空嘅樽，覺得香港示威者算仁慈，因為唔係掟汽油彈，反而你黑警嗰面用呢啲武力去對付示威者，唔對稱。"},{"pid":"87cdb43766d7c2a76d78659e44058f1b543f12d9","tid":1244053,"uid":264368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:53:15.000Z","msg":"唔敢衝但又想出一分力？請團結凝聚力量<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1241997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1241997</a><br />\n---<br />\n依法辦事，保衛人權，守護民眾<br />\n---<br />\n凝聚每個微小力量，召集有勇有謀既義士<br />\n無論你係咩人，你既能力總有一樣我地係需要既<br />\n---<br />\n香港民眾防衛隊<br />\nHong Kong Civil Defence Force<br />\n加入: <a href=\"http://forms.gle/iq4ZtTxfFFRJuPyV8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fiq4ZtTxfFFRJuPyV8&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=9908873f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">forms.gle/iq4ZtTxfFFRJuPyV8</a><br />\n---<br />\nTelegram 聯絡: <a href=\"http://t.me/HKCDF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKCDF&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=6fcfe677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HKCDF</a><br />\nTelegram 資訊: <a href=\"http://t.me/HKCDFInformation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKCDFInformation&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=28cb7716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HKCDFInformation</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/civildefenceforcehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fcivildefenceforcehk&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=29f97f97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/civildefenceforcehk</a>"},{"pid":"cbcc177c0957fd425679a379e60676d3398d64c3","tid":1244053,"uid":190928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f83054c851eecfbab671bd94e3614fddfc9d08b7","tid":1244053,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike